    {
      "bookmarkId": "546339_110_11949-11997",
      "chapterUid": 110,
      "range": "11949-11997",
      "markText": "那天早些时候，我确信无人注意，做了一件二十六年前就已经做过的事情：将一把皱皱的钞票塞在草席下面。",
      "totalCount": 54702,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=546339&chapterUid=110&rangeStart=11949&rangeEnd=11997",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d332e805856230d3bebc23?chapterUid=110&rangeStart=11949&rangeEnd=11997"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "546339_117_2315-2346",
      "chapterUid": 117,
      "range": "2315-2346",
      "markText": "也许每个人心中都有一个风筝，无论它意味着什么，让我们勇敢地追。",
      "totalCount": 39348,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=546339&chapterUid=117&rangeStart=2315&rangeEnd=2346",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d332e805856230d3bebc23?chapterUid=117&rangeStart=2315&rangeEnd=2346"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "546339_98_7252-7263",
      "chapterUid": 98,
      "range": "7252-7263",
      "markText": "“为你，千千万万遍！”",
      "totalCount": 36504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=546339&chapterUid=98&rangeStart=7252&rangeEnd=7263",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d332e805856230d3bebc23?chapterUid=98&rangeStart=7252&rangeEnd=7263"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "546339_116_20879-20897",
      "chapterUid": 116,
      "range": "20879-20897",
      "markText": "“为你，千千万万遍。”我听见自己说。",
      "totalCount": 28500,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=546339&chapterUid=116&rangeStart=20879&rangeEnd=20897",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d332e805856230d3bebc23?chapterUid=116&rangeStart=20879&rangeEnd=20897"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "546339_114_9773-9789",
      "chapterUid": 114,
      "range": "9773-9789",
      "markText": "“为你，千千万万遍。”法里德说。",
      "totalCount": 23154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=546339&chapterUid=114&rangeStart=9773&rangeEnd=9789",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d332e805856230d3bebc23?chapterUid=114&rangeStart=9773&rangeEnd=9789"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "546339_114_3948-4054",
      "chapterUid": 114,
      "range": "3948-4054",
      "markText": "“最严重的创口在上唇。”阿曼德说，“冲击力让你的上唇裂成两半，从人中裂开。不过别担心，整容医师帮你缝好了，他们认为你会恢复得很好，不过那儿会有道伤痕。这可避免不了。“",
